These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, march
2 different games are played: whist, go
1. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Birthday         | march   | september |
| Game   | whist  | go      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Flower    | amaryllis        | balloon-flower    |
| Sport       | surfing         | water-polo |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
