The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, go
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, boat
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing go is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go |
| Transport           | bus        | boat   |

